                        },
                        "description": "<p>Mass spectra were collected on a Thermo Scientific LTQ Orbitrap XL mass spectrometer fitted with a HESIII ionisation source in negative-ion mode. Scan range was 100 - 1500 m/z at a resolution of 60,000 amu in centroid mode with the Orbitrap detector. Heater Temp: 400 \u00b0C; Nitrogen Sheeth Gas Flow rate: 50; Aux\u3000Gas Flow rate: 10; Spray Voltage: 3.5 kV; Capillary Temp: 300 \u00b0C; Spray position (x,y,z): 0,1,C; Lock mass on/off: on; Lock mass (m/z): 391.284286. MS/MS data was collected with the Ion Trap detector with a Coliision Energy of 35%.</p>",
